news.title: Blackstone to sell stake in MGM Grand, Mandalay Bay to VICI Properties
news.para: The deal includes the assumption of Blackstone Real Estate Investment Trust's (BREIT) existing property-level debt that has a principal balance of $3 billion.

news.title: MDH buys Gurgaon land for Rs 120 crore
news.para: “It has bought 20,236 sq metre land in sector 18 Gurgaon for Rs 98 crore and another 1,000 sq metre land for Rs 22 crore in Udyog Vihar in Gurgaon,” said one person aware of the deal.

news.title: Sunac China received $1.69 billion in loans as state steps up support
news.para: The Beijing-based group has been struggling to repay its creditors, and is undergoing a debt restructuring of all its onshore and offshore bonds according to sources, after defaulting on some dollar bonds and extending yuan bonds this year.

news.title: Haryana cabinet nod for land partnership policy
news.para: During the course of project development, land owners will be offered 50% profits out of the running revenue every six months. The time period is three years for projects up to 500 acres and five years for those beyond 500 acres.

news.title: Expert panel recommends blanket ban on construction in Naintial's green zones
news.para: The committee, having officials from the pollution control board, forest department and Kumaon commission, was formed on September 1 after a Nainital resident urged the green watchdog to look into the declining green cover in and around Nainital.

news.title: Assam: 29 towns switch to online mode for building approvals
news.para: The state housing and urban affairs department is initiating the move to bring transparency in building permission at a time when many buildings were allegedly built without proper scientific approval.

news.title: Maharashtra: Property registration revenue at 78% of target till November-end
news.para: High-value property registrations, followed by increased ready reckoner rates and stamp duty charges, have helped the state property registration department achieve 78% of its annual revenue target by the end of November.

news.title: Centrum Housing to acquire National Trust Housing biz in a cash deal
news.para: The deal value could not be immediately ascertained, but the acquisition would be a cash deal, a person familiar with the matter said. The deal is likely to be signed very soon, perhaps in a day or two, the person said.

news.title: SC extends medical bail of ex-statutory auditor of Amrapali Group
news.para: "Counsel for the petitioner states that the counsel who has to address submissions is on his legs in a part-heard matter and ASG appearing on the opposite side was informed though the adjournment letter is not before us.

news.title: Blackstone's $69 billion REIT curbs redemptions in blow to property empire
news.para: The redemption curbs came because they hit pre-set limits, rather than Blackstone setting the limits on the day. Nonetheless, they fueled investor concerns about the future of the REIT, which makes up about 17% of Blackstone's earnings. Blackstone shares ended trading down 7.1% on the news.

news.title: HDFC sells 2.4% shares in Ansal Housing
news.para: This transaction includes sale of 6,24,000 shares representing 1.05% of the paid-up share capital of Ansal Housing done on November 30, 2022.

news.title: Chintels Paradiso owner says will go for another audit before taking down buildings
news.para: It said it has had preliminary discussions with the Central Building Research Institute (CBRI) and Engineers India Limited (EIL) for another structural audit in order to get a second opinion.

news.title: Godrej Properties acquires 18-acre land parcel in Kandivali, Mumbai
news.para: The project will have a developable potential of approximately 3.72 million sq ft with an estimated revenue potential of approximately Rs 7,000 crore.

news.title: Mangaluru city corporation to refloat tenders for LED streetlights project
news.para: Since the project failed to achieve at least 20% progress, even after many deadline extensions, the city corporation has decided to invite tenders again, to install 60,000 LED streetlights in the city.

news.title: Blox raises nearly Rs 100 crore from investors
news.para: The funds will be utilized by the company for market expansion, boosting the product portfolio, and building data infrastructure across customer, broker, and developer segments.
